2005-06-22 21:37:14 GMT	Richard Kettlewell <rjk@greenend.org.uk>	base-0

    Summary:
      release 0.1
    Revision:
      lj2news--mainline--0--base-0

    * ljrss2news: wrapper script which does all the work
    * ljrssexpand.c: program to take an RSS file and split out the elements
      of each item into separate files
    * ljrsstextify: script to convert split-up RSS items into text files
      suitable for posting
    * ljrsspost: script to post converted articles

    new files:
     ChangeLog.d/lj2news--mainline--0 Makefile.am README
     configure.ac ljrss2news ljrssexpand.c ljrsspost ljrsstextify
     prepare


